metadata.name: Abstracted Venus
metadata.description:
7.10.22  
Comes with the original framed pastel 
9x12 inches - Chalk pastel on mixed media paper  
3024 × 4032 - MP4 animation with audio

'Machine Learning' is physical medium renderings of original AI-generated images. I embed myself at every point in the process, from seed image prompts of my own work to the final reproduction. In doing so, the machine and I are learning from each other.
